===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|abundance|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|fro}} {{term|abundance|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|abundantia|lang=la}}, from {{term|abundo|abundō|lang=la}}. See {{term|abound|lang=en}}.

